    <h1>How to Build Muscle After 50<br><span class="green">Without the Gym</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">You don't need a gym to build muscle after 50. But you do need resistance — and most men underestimate what counts. Here's the simple plan that actually works.</p>
    <p style="color:#6ee7a0;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;margin-top:1rem;">The barrier isn't the gym. It's consistency.</p>
    <p style="color:#9ca3af;font-size:0.97rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">Most men aren't low on effort — they're low on protein.</p>
